A SAML metadata document.

```
exampleMetadata

infused
```

Example:

```
provider = iam.SamlProvider(self, "Provider",
    metadata_document=iam.SamlMetadataDocument.from_file("/path/to/saml-metadata-document.xml")
)
principal = iam.SamlPrincipal(provider, {
    "StringEquals": {
        "SAML:iss": "issuer"
    }
})
```

